<div id="wb_element_instance343" class="wb_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>BUENOS AIRES- USHUAIA</strong></h3>

<h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>7 days, 6 nights</strong></h3>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<p> </p>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>The program includes the following services:</strong></h2>

<p> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong>* At Buenos Aires: 3 nights of lodging in the chosen hotel with breakfast.<br>
* Transfers to Airport / Hotel / Airport/<br>
* Tour along the Buenos Aires City<br>
* At Ushuaia: 3 nights of lodging at the chosen hotel with breakfast.<br>
* Transfers Airport / Hotel / Airport.<br>
* Excursion to Tierra del Fuego National Park + Train of the End of the World<br>
* Transfers to Airport / Hotel / Airport/<br>
* Dinner Tango`s Show</strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Day 1: BUENOS AIRES</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Welcome to the Tango's city, we were waiting for you! Once you arrive the International Airport of Ezeiza, you will be taken to the chosen hotel. During the evening it will fulfil a City Tour to take the first contact with the take care.The rest of the day is free to begin feeling the demurrage At night, lodging.</strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Day 2: BUENOS AIRES</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Breakfast. It' s time to enjoy Buenos Aires night life. Lodging.<br>
 </strong></h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Day 3: BUENOS AIRES / USHUAIA</strong></h2>

<p> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Breakfast. Transfer to the airport of The Buenos Aires, and an oath: some day I will return... You will leave toward "The End of the World" and will arrive to the most southern city that you ever visit. Transfer to the selected hotel. The rest of the day is free. Lodging at the hotel.<br>
 </strong></h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Day 4: USHUAIA</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Breakfast and departure to the Tierra del Fuego National Park + Train of the End of the World. There you could see the nature in their maxim expression. And if you want to be more adventurous you could enjoy Full Day Park. And don't desperate, tomorrow you will have many thins to do. Lodging.</strong></h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Day 5: USHUAIA</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Breakfast. The day is completely free, but we know that this sounds not enough. Our suggestion is connected with adventure just to visit Escondido's Lake and Fagnano´s Lake. By night, lodging at the hotel.</strong></h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Day 6: USHUAIA / BUENOS AIRES</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Breakfast. Transfer to Ushuaia´s airport and we assure you: some day you will be return here.<br>
Arrive to Buenos Aires airport. In the night Dinner´s Tango Show at Carlos Gardel Corner.<br>
Lodging at the chosen hotel.</strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong> </strong></h1>

